{"name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Symm","instances":[],"imports":["Lean.Meta.Reduce","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Assert","Lean.Meta.DiscrTree","Lean.Meta.AppBuilder"],"declarations":[{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Symm.lean#L112-L124","name":"Lean.MVarId.symmSaturate","line":112,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Symm.html#Lean.MVarId.symmSaturate","doc":"For every hypothesis `h : a ~ b` where a `@[symm]` lemma is available,\nadd a hypothesis `h_symm : b ~ a`. "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Symm.html#Lean.MVarId.symmSaturate\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">MVarId</span>.<span class=\"name\">symmSaturate</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">g</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Symm.lean#L107-L110","name":"Lean.MVarId.applySymmAt","line":107,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Symm.html#Lean.MVarId.applySymmAt","doc":"Use a symmetry lemma (i.e. marked with `@[symm]`) to replace a hypothesis in a goal. "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Symm.html#Lean.MVarId.applySymmAt\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">MVarId</span>.<span class=\"name\">applySymmAt</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">h</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.FVarId\">FVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">g</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Symm.lean#L87-L105","name":"Lean.MVarId.applySymm","line":87,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Symm.html#Lean.MVarId.applySymm","doc":"Apply a symmetry lemma (i.e. marked with `@[symm]`) to a metavariable.\n\nThe type of `g` should be of the form `a ~ b`, and is used to index the symm lemmas.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Symm.html#Lean.MVarId.applySymm\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">MVarId</span>.<span class=\"name\">applySymm</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">g</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Symm.lean#L68-L81","name":"Lean.Expr.applySymm","line":68,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Symm.html#Lean.Expr.applySymm","doc":"Given a term `e : a ~ b`, construct a term in `b ~ a` using `@[symm]` lemmas. "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Symm.html